snippet.textDisplay: Total song is so soothing and beautiful. May be I have listened this song over 20 times. I just love to play this song now and then. I must say, Pakistan's music industry is really rich in quality.Abida Sultana ji, Momina, Rahat Fateh ali khan, Zeb and Haniya,Shuja Haider, Noori band..lots of names. I can't write all names. All are my favorite. I think MUSIC can break all kinds of barrier. I mean it. I would love to listen more beautiful songs from Coke Studio in future. Thanks to all of the people who work so hard behind the execution of this type of song. So that we can get more and more  beautiful, mind blowing, soothing, soul touching songs. You people are super awesome.
